{"tid":742572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（放負叫春長文慎入）趁後生有機會真係要拍一次拖，唔好驚","createTime":"2018-07-14T16:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T07:27:41.000Z","uid":193492,"like":26,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8a054467b1b14b675f80b22b11ca2770ea51b6f8","tid":742572,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"認真，大人成日剩係識講中學拍拖影響學業，大學先拍拖都唔遲；但係就冇諗過人生中呢段時間係最開心比較無優無慮、自己仲係純真但係都開始成長少少成熟、最正既時候。<br />\n<br />\n自己細個喺好保守家教好嚴既屋企長大。爸媽成日講到好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （咩撘人膊頭俾人告性騷擾又未婚懷孕etc)所以我由細到大同異性相處都一句起兩句止就住就住，甚至可以話係直情怕咗。去到grad嗰日，我影相都真係冇撘人膊頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁當然我唔係賴父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己有責任，只能怪自己太聽話唔識思考，或且都唔夠自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （但係唔知點解我同啲女仔正常講嘢又冇事，甚至可以去到講笑做到閏蜜到而家都仲有聯絡；但係當我想追人既時候就唔知點解好多嘢顧慮好驚好尷尬）<br />\n<br />\n到上到大學，以為係天堂可以擺脫單身；點知個個都一係就有仔，一係就A十幾廿幾，都冇興趣同你個唔熟既A0死毒撚講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲甚至唔係處...<br />\n<br />\n世界唔會停，時間照過人繼續生活，而自己就停左望住人地各有各精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉，好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己主動試過玩交友app攞到人地SC IG，但係過左無幾耐又冇哂下文（一係人地已讀不回，一係自己頹得濟覺得自己想搵水泡為追而追於是又靜咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ））<br />\n<br />\n所以後生有機會真係要拍一次拖，唔好有太多顧慮，攞定經驗同信心；如果唔係就好似我咁就黎20都仲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （純粹放負，請大家屌細力啲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f6784e99d7854138fa1f2c0d0214a182fc7f1d","tid":742572,"uid":146435,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"閣下樣子如何？"},{"pid":"403512d11b4144731193c109c9ce93fe0cf2b77e","tid":742572,"uid":26179,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"平心而論，你樣衰啫<br />\n好樣嘅啲女主動埋嚟你有得唔拍咩"},{"pid":"aa598893c11928e0fe597fb83742cecf71fcb885","tid":742572,"uid":105863,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"20都未有就係到叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8558035c20efed1735d84abba2992ac17e911d18","tid":742572,"uid":193492,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"403512d11b4144731193c109c9ce93fe0cf2b77e","tid":742572,"uid":26179,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"平心而論，你樣衰啫<br />\n好樣嘅啲女主動埋嚟你有得唔拍咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"我都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我又諗，如果我樣真係衰到女仔怕左我又點解會識到女仔friend(仲要有啲係好close會同我講自己屋企嘢感情嘢）？呢啲唔係剩係因為樣既問題咁簡單掛"},{"pid":"76c4768ddc72ba0f3f57274bb31c1064a2c3197d","tid":742572,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aa598893c11928e0fe597fb83742cecf71fcb885","tid":742572,"uid":105863,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"20都未有就係到叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"望到周圍身邊...唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e1b3dad24079c85fe5f253392b64aa20307d9c","tid":742572,"uid":105863,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76c4768ddc72ba0f3f57274bb31c1064a2c3197d","tid":742572,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aa598893c11928e0fe597fb83742cecf71fcb885","tid":742572,"uid":105863,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"20都未有就係到叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"望到周圍身邊...唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"我係女都唔要你啦<br />\n7到要生要死咁<br />\n<br />\n利申：25A0"},{"pid":"744f3b